# === Notes ===
# fd respects .gitignore files by default
# This file is in addition to .gitignore
# Use fd --hidden to search hidden files
# Use fd --no-ignore to ignore all ignore files (including .gitignore)
# Use fd --unrestricted to show everything (same as --hidden --no-ignore)
